headline: Visa's tech stack powers BUUT's bold new card for Gen Z
summary: Visa and Pismo have teamed up with ABN AMRO to power BUUT's challenger card targeted at Gen Z consumers. BUUT's debit card was created in just 10 weeks using Pismo's cloud-native platform, demonstrating how traditional financial institutions can move at fintech speed when powered by the right technology partner.
